### product list
GET http://localhost:{{$dotenv PORT}}/products

### product by id
@productId = 248e7548-5198-4cc1-a794-44d275f0b63c
GET http://localhost:{{$dotenv PORT}}/products/{{productId}}

### product create1
POST http://localhost:{{$dotenv PORT}}/products/create
Content-Type: application/json; charset=UTF-8
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv ACCESS_TOKEN}}

{
    "name": "psk Wooden Gloves",
    "description": "this is my create Usus aduro vomito consuasor voveo valens. Molestiae enim bos aranea. Deprecator neque excepturi ventus tot claudeo.",
    "price": 18239,
    "tags":[
        {"name":"psk"},
        {"name":"glove"},
        {"name":"wood"}
    ]
}

### product create2
POST http://localhost:{{$dotenv PORT}}/products/create
Content-Type: application/json; charset=UTF-8
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv ACCESS_TOKEN}}

{
