### product update
PATCH http://localhost:{{$dotenv PORT}}/products/{{productId}}/update
Content-Type: application/json; charset=UTF-8
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv ACCESS_TOKEN}}

{
    "name": "psk new Gloves",
    "description": "my glove is perfect!! 100% protect your hand from cold!",
    "price": 99999,
    "tags":[
        {"name":"psk"},
        {"name":"100% warming"},
        {"name":"new"},
        {"name":"my hands!"}
    ]
}

### product delet
DELETE http://localhost:{{$dotenv PORT}}/products/{{productId}}/delete
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv ACCESS_TOKEN}}